    <p id="Par13">Before giving details on gsufsort implementation, we briefly recall some data structures definitions. For a string <italic>S</italic> of length <italic>n</italic> let the suffix starting at position <italic>i</italic> be denoted <inline-formula id="IEq25"><alternatives><tex-math id="M49">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
