				\begin{document}$${{\mathsf {S}}}{{\mathsf {A}}}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M54"><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="sans-serif">S</mml:mi><mml:mi mathvariant="sans-serif">A</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="13015_2020_177_Article_IEq27.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> of a string <italic>S</italic> of length <italic>n</italic> is an array with a permutation of <inline-formula id="IEq28"><alternatives><tex-math id="M55">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
