    <p id="Par14">gsufsort uses algorithm g<sc>SACA-K</sc> [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR10">10</xref>] to construct <inline-formula id="IEq44"><alternatives><tex-math id="M87">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
