    <p id="Par16">We compared our tool and mkESA. mkESA [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR17">17</xref>] is a fast suffix array construction software designed for bioinformatics applications.</p>
    <p id="Par17">We ran both versions of our tool, gsufsort and gsufsort-light, to build arrays <inline-formula id="IEq70"><alternatives><tex-math id="M137">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
