    <p id="Par19">The collections we used in our experiments are described in Table <xref rid="Tab1" ref-type="table">1</xref>. They comprise real DNAs, real proteins, documents, random DNA and random protein, and differ by their alphabet size and also by the maximum and average <inline-formula id="IEq74"><alternatives><tex-math id="M145">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
