    <p id="Par26">The memory ratio (bytes/N) of gsufsort and gsufsort-light is constant, 21 and 17 bytes per input symbol respectively, corresponding to the space of the input string <italic>T</italic> (<italic>N</italic> bytes) plus the space for arrays <inline-formula id="IEq88"><alternatives><tex-math id="M157">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
